parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag sensor can cause the airbag to not deploy in the event of a crash, leading to increased risk of injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
the airbag sensor light intermittently illuminates
the airbag fails to deploy in a crash
the passenger seat sensor fails to detect a passenger.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger seat occupancy sensor can cause the airbag to not deploy in the event of a crash, leading to increased risk of injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
the passenger seat sensor fails to detect a passenger
the airbag fails to deploy in a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbag to not deploy in the event of a crash, leading to increased risk of injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag fails to deploy in a crash
the airbag warning light illuminates
the airbag sensor light intermittently illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent failure of the speedometer can cause the driver to lose track of their speed, leading to potential accidents or traffic violations.
symptoms: The speedometer works intermittently
sometimes showing incorrect speeds
sometimes not working at all
and occasionally showing 0 mph even when the vehicle is moving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The electrical system malfunctions can cause various safety issues, including failure of essential systems, such as the speedometer, fuel gauge, and temperature gauge, and can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The electrical system malfunctions
causing issues such as: speedometer
fuel gauge
and temperature gauge providing inaccurate readings
blinker lights flashing rapidly
radio scanning stations continuously
battery dying
and windows not working intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The dealer service issues can cause frustration and delay in resolving the problems, leading to potential safety risks and financial losses for the vehicle owner.
symptoms: Dealers refusing to perform repairs
citing unusual reasons
such as only doing oil changes on weekends
and not providing rental cars for repairs
leading to delays and unresolved issues.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering system can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries, as the vehicle may pull to one side or become difficult to maneuver.
symptoms: The steering wheel becomes difficult to turn
the vehicle pulls to one side
the steering wheel shakes or vibrates
a grinding or rubbing noise is heard from the steering
the vehicle loses control
and the airbags may not deploy in the event of a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the tie rod can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries, as the vehicle may pull to one side or become difficult to maneuver.
symptoms: The vehicle pulls to one side
the steering wheel becomes difficult to turn
a popping or clunking sound is heard from the front end
and the tie rod snaps.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause injuries or fatalities in the event of a crash, as the airbags may not deploy.
symptoms: The airbags do not deploy in the event of a crash
and the passenger airbag system fails.
